Package mlflex.tcga

Class Summary
AbstractTcgaDataProcessor This abstract class is designed to provide support for all data processors that use TCGA data.
ChromosomeBandMetadataProcessor This class parses cytogenetic band locations from a UCSC metadata file.
GenePositionMetadataProcessor This class parses gene locations from a UCSC metadata file.
TcgaAgeDataProcessor This data processor is designed to parse information from the TCGA clinical data; specifically, it handles age data.
TcgaCghLevel3DataProcessor This data processor parses gene-level data for Agilent CGH arrays for data from The Cancer Genome Atlas.
TcgaCghMetadataProcessor This class supports processing of metadata that describes probes used in Agilent CGH arrays.
TcgaChromosomeCopyNumberDataProcessor This data processor parses chromosome-level data for Agilent CGH arrays for data from The Cancer Genome Atlas.
TcgaClinicalDataProcessor This data processor is designed to parse information from the TCGA clinical data; specifically, it handles "age," "gender" and "KPS" data.
TcgaClinicalTabDataParser This class is designed to parse the tab-delimited files with clinical data in The Cancer Genome Atlas.
TcgaCopyNumberLevel3DataProcessor This data processor parses chromosome-level data for Illumina SNP arrays for data from The Cancer Genome Atlas.
TcgaHistologyDataProcessor This data processor is designed to parse information from the TCGA clinical data; specifically, it handles histology data.
TcgaMethylationLevel2DataProcessor This data processor is designed to parse DNA methylation data from TCGA formatted files; specifically, it parses files in the "Level 2" format, which contains probe-level values.
TcgaMethylationMeanDataProcessor This data processor is designed to parse DNA methylation data from TCGA formatted files; specifically, it parses files in the "Level 2" format, which contains probe-level values.
TcgaMethylationMetadataProcessor This data processor is designed to parse metadata information to support parsing of DNA methylation data in TCGA; specifically, it supports a conversion of probe identifiers to gene symbols.
TcgaMiRnaLevel3DataProcessor This data processor is designed to parse microRNA (miRNA) expression data from TCGA formatted files; specifically, it parses files in the "Level 3" format.
TcgaMrnaLevel2DataProcessor This data processor is designed to parse mRNA expression data from TCGA formatted files; specifically, it parses files in the "Level 2" format, which contains probeset-level summarizations.
TcgaMrnaLevel3DataProcessor This data processor is designed to parse mRNA expression data from TCGA formatted files; specifically, it parses files in the "Level 3" format, which contains gene-level summarizations.
TcgaMrnaMetadataProcessor This data processor is designed to parse metadata information to support parsing of mRNA expression data in TCGA; specifically, it supports a conversion of probeset identifiers to gene symbols.
TcgaRadiationDependentVariableDataProcessor This data processor is designed to parse information from the TCGA clinical data; specifically, it indicates whether each patient received radiation treament.
TcgaSomaticMutationDataProcessor This data processor is designed to parse information from the TCGA somatic-mutation data.
TcgaSurvivalDataProcessor This data processor is designed to parse information from the TCGA clinical data; specifically, it handles survival data.
TcgaTreatmentsDataProcessor This data processor is designed to parse information from the TCGA clinical data; specifically, it handles treatment data.
TwoYearSurvivalTransformer This class is design for machine-learning analyses that are designed to predict survival status.
